title: Duane Barry - Cosmic Refractions On DanceRadioGlobal.com #2 26-4
description:
Hey everyone, I'm pleased to present the second installment of my Cosmic Refractions radio show broadcast on DanceRadioGlobal.

A selection of my favourite tunes of the month, the hour starts with some beautiful melodies courtesy of East Cafe and Coalesced remixes and an exclusive track from Abdomen Burst forthcoming on Silk Digital. Afterwards we descend into some harder tracks with stomping beats and basslines before continuing with the progressive edge with a new track from myself, a stunning remix by Retroid and the hugely popular cheesy but great "Guestlist" track!

Finally, we close with the gloriously old skool laced summer anthem from C83.

I hope you enjoy my show this month and please check out my myspace for any further info about me :)

Tracklist:

1. Jacco@Work - Hashcake (East Cafe Breaks Mix) [LuPS]
2. Faskil - Rezi (Coalesced Remix) [Silk Digital]
3. Abdomen Burst - Sky In Your Hands (Original Mix) [Silk Digital]
4. Lunar Shift - Come Alive (Ways And Means Remix) [Ego Shot]
5. DJ Mutiny - Dreams Come True (BSD Remix) [iBreaks]
6. BreakZhead Feat. Detach - Paranoid Vibe (Original Mix) [Subtribe]
7. Duane Barry - Cerulean Blue (Original Mix) [Flextone]
8. Vibespirit - I Like Girls Do It (Original Mix) [13Breaks]
9. Parrket - Fuckin Use The Crystal (Retroid Remix) [Morphosis]
10. WoNK - Nasty Dog (Karl Sav Remix) [Destination?]
11. Sporty-O Feat. Keith Mac - Guestlist (Keith Mackenzie & Fixx VS Angel Alanis Mix) [Rat Records]
12. C83 Feat. Liz Melody - When We Were Young (Original Mix) [En:Vision]
